.: Plot :.
After being abducted by a creepy middle-aged man, Kate Walker, 30, awakens to find herself in a small chamber with wall-to-wall bloodstained cracked tiles. The room looks like it could be part of a long-forgotten asylum, or worse. There is a large locked steel door on one wall. The door opens, and Kate and 19 other people emerge from adjacent chambers...

The group soon discovers that they each have been abducted and placed into a nightmarish labyrinth where they are nothing more than sport for unearthly demon-like creatures that stalk and kill their human prey
